title: Hour 1 - Preseason Deshaun Watson, Woodstock Reminisces
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Preseason Deshaun Watson, Woodstock Reminisces
description:
Dan is surprised the Browns are starting Deshaun Watson in their preseason game tomorrow. And he and the Danettes reminisce about their personal experiences (or lack thereof) at the fable Woodstock concerts over the years.
